summary: Aiming to bring forward and implement new developments in cardiology, which benefit our patients. Expierenced in clinical and experimental studies, involving molecular and genetic pathways of myocardial remodeling, fibrosis, diabetes, cardio-oncology, and genetics of heart failure.
